JOHANNESBURG - Newly appointed police minister Fikile Mbalula has vowed to take a serious stance against criminals and has promised to put lawbreakers behind bars for a long time but the man also known as Razzmatazz has definitely not lost his sense of humor since moving into the new job.During a media briefing on Tuesday, Mbalula had many in stitches when he asked a man sitting next to him to open a bottle of water for him.The man did as instructed, but first took a sip.*Watch Mbalula s reaction in the video above.eNCA